{"id": "1423584124450639904", "channel_id": "1423584124450639904", "type": 0, "author_id": "1404429694723555339", "author_name": "yuxue641", "author_bot": false, "content": "PVP哈姆林4费30伤害，和杜勒3费30伤比多出一费（一模一样的伤害卡为什么多一费，哪怕加个奇妙效果，做点差异化也行）\n和莉兹5费32伤害比，莉兹有预备还有单体0费强化，相比之下哈姆林4费35伤害本来就会在手里卡好几回合，削伤害更打不出去了。 \n\n直接砍掉大招流血机制相当于是削了哈姆林近一半伤害，已经算是大削了。  \n3费毕竟给了两迟缓，参考汀克特的3费全体一迟缓，和弥利亚姆的给的迟缓，从给迟缓的角度来看是公平的。但伤害建议7或者8伤害对标同类迟缓卡。\n\n鉴于不少红卡角色都削了，但是至少别出现一模一样的卡还比别人多一费这种问题<:takenotes:1357186646294138890> \n显得削得很…潦草（？）", "timestamp": "2025-10-03T08:15:04.183000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1423584125306011710", "filename": "IMG_4156.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 626650, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423584124450639904/1423584125306011710/IMG_4156.png?ex=69cc2b48&is=69cad9c8&hm=033911231dc1e9a661ef26d1a3334a5914855daef0d8265e3dadb8fbf5245a83&"}, {"id": "1423584125792682085", "filename": "IMG_4157.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 625573, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423584124450639904/1423584125792682085/IMG_4157.png?ex=69cc2b48&is=69cad9c8&hm=a285288f1113ba159a7885249f5a95196bd113157b0296a95152a014e13c710e&"}, {"id": "1423584126082224138", "filename": "IMG_4159.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 544618, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423584124450639904/1423584126082224138/IMG_4159.png?ex=69cc2b48&is=69cad9c8&hm=ce4f7301fd73797519d8830daa33d00811027c6efd2b940c5c2e720901a5b398&"}, {"id": "1423584126421696574", "filename": "IMG_4160.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1103589, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423584124450639904/1423584126421696574/IMG_4160.png?ex=69cc2b48&is=69cad9c8&hm=e7270c226342d6377087e8ab3d9769e275b06f915464fc20f573552f039ce97d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423584124450639904", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "感觉削过头了？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823